POLKADOT:

POST request at https://polkadot.api.subscan.io/api/scan/staking/validators
	Filter by using stash_account_display -> display -> luganodes
	For that object -> bonded_total
	Divide the number by -> 1,340,519,708
	Multiply by 100 to get percentage of staked tokens
	
	
Kusama:

POST request at https://kusama.api.subscan.io/api/scan/staking/validators
	Filter by using stash_account_display -> display -> luganodes
	For that object -> bonded_total
	Divide the number by -> 9,651,217
	Multiply by 100 to get percentage of staked tokens
